<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV77">
<l>tiṅkaḷam piḷḷai pulampattaṉ ceṅkō laracupaṭṭa</l>
<l>ceṅkaḷam paṟṟiniṉ ṟeḷkupuṉ mālaiteṉ pālilaṅkai</l>
<l>veṅkaḷañ ceytanam viṇṇōr pirāṉār tuḻāytuṇaiyā</l>
<l>naṅkaḷai māmaikoḷ vāṉvantu tōṉṟi nalikiṉṟatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Bleak evening who constantly slights [us], seizing [us] on the red battle field,</l>
<l>where the red-sceptered king fell, for the moon child to be lonely, as a companion</l>
<l>to the Tulsi of our lord of celestials who made a hot battle field in Laṅkā in the South,</l> 
<l>in order to take [our] dark complexion it turns up [and] afflicts us.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
